data.description: SELLER OFFERING 2% TOWARD BUYDOWN OF INTEREST RATE OR CONCESSIONS!!!!! Beautiful 4 bedroom/2 bathroom nestled on a large acer with horse privileges and NO HOA. Highly upgraded cabinets throughout, quartz countertops in the kitchen & bathrooms,  20'' tile throughout and carpet in all the right places. Skylights in the living room and kitchen to give the home a lot of warm natural light. Boasting 3 car garage up front and at least 6 car driveway.There is a detached 2 car garage in the back yard, also with a 2 car slab. Best part is it has a 1/2 bath so you don't have to come in if your working in the garage. This garage could also be used as storage if needed. Water run to all trees. The back yard is ready for you to make your resort getaway and add the horse stalls and horses.
